body_html:
@avantol Have you tried following the instructions here to build TF on your pi:
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/master/tensorflow/contrib/pi_examples
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/master/tensorflow/contrib/makefile#raspberry-pi

Note that *.pb.h files are generated by the protocol buffer compiler. That's where to start looking wrt problems with your install.
